working on an activity.

B. True
Answer: A
Which of the following situations causes the creation of a hijacked file?
A. A version in a snapshot view is modified without first being checked out.
B. A version in a dynamic view is modified without firstbeing checked out.
C. A version in a snapshot view is checked out and renamed.
D. A version in a dynamic view is checked out and renamed.
Answer: A
